results.name: A000012 * A002865 as a diagonalized matrix.
comment: Row sums = the partition numbers, A000041: (1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 15,...).
formula: A000012 * A002865 as a diagonalized matrix, the latter = an infinite lower triangular matrix with A002865: (1, 0, 1, 1, 2, 2, 4, 4, 7, 8,...) as the main diagonal and the rest zeros. Triangle read by rows, n-th row = first (n+1) terms of A002865.
